text: Davaagiin Enkhee (born 29 July 1964) is a Mongolian cross-country skier. She competed at the 1988 Winter Olympics and the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Mongolian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Mongolia Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1988 Winter Olympics Category:Cross- country skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:People from Uvs Province
